<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>علينا) <span class="c2">(٢)</span> حرج أن <span class="c2">(ننام)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> قبل صلاة العشاء؟<span class="c5"> قال:</span> نعم وحرج <span class="c2">(وحرجان)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> وثلاثة <span class="c2">(أحرج)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
